{"tid":1920888,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家知唔知手足遭受緊嘅，係點樣嘅酷刑？","createTime":"2020-03-11T18:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T10:04:17.000Z","uid":305602,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0a3087ff2d612f76073c3254ba0d518d47b1b6fc","tid":1920888,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0RFcao0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0RFcao0.png&h=c479ea27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信大家都知道好多手足俾人捉左入去之後，都被迫屈打成招，其中有人會怪手足做「所謂污點證人」篤灰，但係其實無入過去根本就好難想像手足經歷緊咩<br />\n<br />\n就此<br />\n我係到想同大家介紹一套韓國電影「南營洞1985」，睇完之後，你就會知手足受到點樣既折磨，甚至乎更恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dYM3g5G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdYM3g5G.png&h=58cc4b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先，男主角係跟班狗協助調查嘅時候，突然俾人帶到去南營洞，即係香港嘅新屋嶺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wuQjzSS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwuQjzSS.png&h=64e22ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到個到，可能10日先有一次飯食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5B16ZjQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5B16ZjQ.png&h=6b23a728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔單止咁，男主角仲要日日夜夜受到不同程度嘅折磨<br />\n其中包括水刑、電刑、棍打、唔俾訓覺等等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yfhucFn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyfhucFn.png&h=311e6670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加左辣椒粉嘅水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CUmiQsi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCUmiQsi.png&h=cc668623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0zixasp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0zixasp.png&h=a91f0631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電到幾乎無哂知覺<br />\n<br />\n建議大家睇返原片<br />\n<br />\n介紹呢套電影既目的，在於希望大家能夠明白手足既苦況，有時佢哋都係身不由己，唔係大家三言兩語就明白得到，我地應該要做既就係盡全力支援佢地，彌補返佢地嘅所遭受嘅痛楚，緊記手足為我地做過既野，絕唔能夠對以往到依加發生嘅野而感到盲目，堅守五大訴求，直到香港光復既一天來臨！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"4b849d516403ada81bee9018968d6ccb95a85d5e","tid":1920888,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:07:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9cc395a3a3098e62ccc68d1fbcf12f922a3deeb","tid":1920888,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:07:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a61f87217830c43fd72d1ee74afc4b31b37ebfc2","tid":1920888,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:07:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96300339116e1ed94bcb15a36986f10dc052f419","tid":1920888,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:07:58.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"4df11e4071eb4d0ba2b53e44a6c229e8437561f4","tid":1920888,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:08:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d5b1c8fe56b5faaddfb08e7a43024dcc93786a7","tid":1920888,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:08:42.000Z","msg":"唉 唔止"},{"pid":"830797ab43a53251fb27febef14022715f89469b","tid":1920888,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96300339116e1ed94bcb15a36986f10dc052f419","tid":1920888,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:07:58.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:09:06.000Z","msg":"唔該手足幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9108c932e0e1fa503d098f750a10f34a0ccdc843","tid":1920888,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:09:21.000Z","msg":"好心痛"},{"pid":"3bdeb599b79a796dd253dcf103f3869085a0c76a","tid":1920888,"uid":50931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:09:33.000Z","msg":"講閪咩，班賤種連登乞票狗話手足唔捱得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407207de32532193d77db769675c88ffc4ed8179","tid":1920888,"uid":167567,"li